Check in was easy, as was check out.	From check in to check out, everything was great.	There are no connecting rooms at this hotel which I specifically asked for when I made the reservation and was not told they just didn't have them.	The hotel reservation desk was OK when we check in but when we checked out it was a different story.	If you have time, check them out.	Check in process was very pleasant, room was nice and CLEAN!!